			<p style="margin-bottom:14.0pt; margin:0cm 0cm 8pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><span lang="EN-AU" style="font-size:10.0pt" xml:lang="EN-AU"><span style="font-family:&quot;Lucida Sans Unicode&quot;,sans-serif">We may sometimes use your personal information (e.g. your IP address) to measure use of our websites and assess the effectiveness of our site pages, including advertising on our sites. We may also use this personal information to improve the content of our websites and services.</span></span></span></span></span></p>
			</td>
